---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import Heading from '../components/Heading.astro';
---

<Layout title="Music Education | Kaitlin Isaac">
  <Header />
  <main id="main" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 py-16 space-y-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
      <Heading 
        level={1}
        class="text-center"
      >
        Music Education
      </Heading>
      
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        As a former middle school band teacher, I'm passionate about music education and ensuring all students 
        have access to quality music learning experiences. Here you'll find resources, insights, and my philosophy 
        on music education.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy Section -->
    <Section title="My Philosophy" backgroundColor="primary">
      <div class="space-y-md">
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          I believe that music education is essential for the complete development of every child. Music teaches 
          creativity, discipline, teamwork, and provides a unique way to express emotions and ideas.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          My approach to music education centers on creating inclusive, engaging environments where students 
          of all backgrounds and ability levels can thrive and develop a lifelong love of music.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- Resources Section -->
    <Section title="Resources" backgroundColor="secondary">
      <div class="space-y-md">
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          I'm in the process of developing resources for music educators, students, and parents. Check back soon for:
        </p>
        
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Lesson plans and teaching materials</li>
          <li>Instrument care guides</li>
          <li>Practice strategies for students</li>
          <li>Music technology resources</li>
          <li>Advocacy materials for music programs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout> 